message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this great product. I think it would be perfect for you. I'm asking for $15,000 to start the negotiations. What do you think?
I'm really interested in the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $10,000. Is that something we could work with?
I appreciate your interest, Bob.  While $10,000 is a bit too low for me, I'm willing to come down to $13,500. I believe this product will bring you a lot of value.
I appreciate your flexibility, but I'm still a bit short on budget. Would you be willing to meet me at $11,500?
